{
  "chapter": 194,
  "chapter_summary": "第194章'董家酒楼'讲述寇仲与徐子陵应宋鲁之邀，至洛阳董家酒楼南厅赴宴。宋鲁携伴侣柳菁、女儿宋玉致等候，酒楼老板董方是宋鲁三十多年老友。席间董方透露洛阳首富荣凤祥订了西厅，宴请吐谷浑王子伏骞和知世郎王薄，李世民与突利则订了东厅，各方势力齐聚。徐子陵迟到，途中巧遇云玉真，得知王薄已与宇文化及秘密结盟，正全力拉拢伏骞。云玉真将此讯息告知徐子陵后离去。回到南厅，众人讨论荣凤祥来历神秘、武功高强。徐子陵透露自己已往净念禅院会见师妃暄，师妃暄因和氏璧已被吞食且寇徐二人是阴癸派大敌，遂放过此事。宋鲁分析南方形势：沈法兴和杜伏威坐大，萧铣兵力增至四十万，威胁宋阀与巴陵帮联盟。寇仲询问竹花帮近况，宋玉致告知其儿时玩伴桂锡良已成新帮主邵令周的快婿。正谈间，顶层传来巨响，伏骞长笑出手，好戏即将上演。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "柳菁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "小仲来哩！竟长得这么高大。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "士别三日，刮目相看，想不到我宋鲁一向自负目光过人，亦对两位看走眼。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang",
      "speaker_name": "董方",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇爷肯赏面光临，乃我董家酒楼荣幸。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "自当年一别，随即得闻君绰的噩耗，人生无常，令人难以排遣。幸好你两人终不负君绰的期望，想她在天之灵，定感安慰。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "柳菁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "今天只准说高兴的话，小仲快罚你鲁叔一杯。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang",
      "speaker_name": "董方",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "仲爷坐下先喝口热茶再说，徐爷不是和你一道来吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "董方是董家酒楼的大老板，在洛阳无人不识，也是我宋鲁三十多年的老朋友，都是自己人，不用客气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小陵他随后便来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "柳菁",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang",
      "text": "董老不是想练站功吧？为何不肯坐下。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang",
      "speaker_name": "董方",
      "listener": "char_liu_jing",
      "text": "为了赚两顿饭糊口，我是天生的辛苦命。今天不知刮的甚么风，三个厢厅都给不能不打个招呼的贵客订了。唉！夫人该知道我坐下来便再不愿起身的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang",
      "text": "董老板真风趣，只不知李世民那小子订的是那一个厢厅呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你刚才没撞见他吗？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "我撞到的是突利，李小子约了他在这里共进午膳。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang",
      "speaker_name": "董方",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "秦王本想订这个厅子的，因可俯瞰天津桥一带的美景，但我早预留给鲁兄，当然不能答应他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "柳菁",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang",
      "text": "那他该是移师西厅，那处也可看到部份天津桥和朝西苑方向流去的洛河景致。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang",
      "speaker_name": "董方",
      "listener": "char_liu_jing",
      "text": "西厅也给人抢先一步订了，所以秦王只能屈就东厅，尚幸那里虽看不到天津桥，仍有洛河东段的景色可供观赏。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang",
      "text": "谁人如此有面子？照我所知，董老板是为了怕来自各地的贵人临时订不到最高层的厢厅，宁可空着也不愿随便给人预订了呢。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang",
      "speaker_name": "董方",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "鲁兄确是小弟肚内的蛔虫，我一向抱着广交天下英雄豪杰的心意，故那一方都不想开罪。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "柳菁",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang",
      "text": "那么谁做皇帝，我们的董老板都可大做生意了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang",
      "text": "董叔尚未交待究竟谁要了西厅哩！",
      "tone": "微嗔",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang",
      "speaker_name": "董方",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "订的人是我们洛阳首富荣凤祥大老板，他要招呼的客人是'知世郎'王薄和来自吐谷浑的王子伏骞，你说我敢否要他们换厅子呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今趟有好戏看了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_ke",
      "speaker_name": "知客",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "宋爷订的南厅在顶楼的四厅十二房中首屈一指，名闻全市。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "text": "又会这么巧的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你是愈长愈俊，寇仲却是愈大愈坏。你两人若可作点交换就好了！寇仲有没有告诉你曾见到为师呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "师傅有个重要的消息告诉你：王薄已与宇文化及秘密结盟，现在更全力拉拢伏骞，希望能借助吐谷浑这新兴的力量来打天下。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "text": "果有此事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "师傅就算要骗任何人，都舍不得骗子陵你。不过伏骞此人城府极深，今趟到中原来主要是了解形势，绝不曾轻率地靠往任何一方的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "text": "师傅你不是刚抵洛阳吗？究竟是从何处得知这么多秘密讯息？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "text": "玉真！你与谁在说话？还不快来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "来了！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "迟些再来找你们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "对荣凤祥这个人，鲁叔有多少认识呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "荣凤祥本身来历神秘，虽从没有人见过他出手，但亦没有人不认为他武功高强。兼之他为人圆滑，故在黑白两道都很吃得开。你以乎很在意他呢？",
      "tone": "冷然",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "柳菁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "小仲你究竟在甚么方面开罪了致致，累得我们都要捱受她的冷言冷语。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_liu_jing",
      "text": "菁姨！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "女儿家爱使性子闹玩儿，如此才见情趣。是了！荣凤祥跟今天是否有好戏看，两者为何会扯上关系？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "荣凤祥这家伙该和李小子有点关系，今次在此宴请伏骞和王薄亦非像表面般简单。只看李小子订的厅厢的时间紧接在荣凤祥之后，便不难看出李世民和突利两个小子都是冲着伏骞、王薄而来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "柳菁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "小仲仍是童心未泯，甚么小家伙大小子的，想笑死人家吗！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这么说，李世民和突利的目标该是伏骞，此人在中原尚未有根基，所以倘能折辱他一番，他便只有黯然而退的结局。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "柳菁",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "小陵的样子变得比小仲更厉害，清秀中透出挺拔不群的英雄气概，谁家女子能不为你倾心呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_liu_jing",
      "text": "菁姨亦是美艳更胜从前呢。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这种动听逗人的话，竟是从小陵之口说出来，真教人难以相信。可知乃是有感而发。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你滚到那里去了？竟敢迟到。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "有甚么地方好去，只不过是到净念禅院打了个转，跟师妃暄说了几句话儿，哈！为甚么要那样瞪着我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你是否把事情全招了出来呢？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "丑妇终须见翁姑，把事情拖着于你我有甚么好处？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你现在是否表面看来虽似好人一个，其实却是受了严重内伤，随时会倒地暴毙？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "柳菁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "去你的，这么不吉利的话也可说出来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "所以常说你是以小人之心去度人家君子之腹，方外人岂会动辄讲打喊杀。那纯是王薄从中弄鬼，刚才我碰到云帮主，证实王薄真的靠拢了我们的大仇人宇文化及，故……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "师妃暄有甚么话说？有没有恐吓你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你这小人之心的习惯何时才能改掉？人家修的是禅法，专讲因果机缘，岂同我们这两个俗人般有仇必报。唉！真恨不得可立即去把宇文化及的臭头割下来送酒。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "恩怨分明有甚么不好？佛门也有除妖降魔的说法。宇文化及这种人若当上皇帝，为害处会不下于杨广。是了！了空怎会那么轻易让你见到师妃暄的？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "我本也以为见不到师妃暄，已准备离开，谁知师妃暄却亲身来会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "柳菁",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "难道她看上你了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这正是我要说的话。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这想法只能是自作多情，师妃暄是个带发修行的方外人，关心的惟有是万民的福祉。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "但她仍没理由肯放过你的？是否你把和氏璧还了给她呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "和氏璧已给我们当饭般吃了，何来宝璧还给她？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "没有一句是正经的，不跟你说。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "我寇仲若有一字虚言，罚我这一世也得不到三小姐的青睐，不信可问你认为老实可靠的陵小子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "小陵不妨来说说这是甚么一回事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "异宝果然是异宝，竟会有此情况出现，教人意想难及。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "柳菁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你两个幸运的小子。",
      "tone": "羡慕",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "今天我不喝酒。",
      "tone": "冷然",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我自己来，不用劳烦你的贵手。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "名传千古的和氏璧既已报销，而你们又是阴癸派的大敌，那师妃暄放开此事，乃明智之举。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "现时南方形势如何呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "柳菁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你还敢问我们？把南方搞得天翻地覆后，你两个便一走了之，留下个烂摊子要人家去收拾。",
      "tone": "嗔怪",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "幸好这烂摊子对我们有利无害。不过美中不足处是沈法兴和杜伏威都因林士宏被削弱实力之后而坐大，直接威胁到我们岭南宋家和巴陵帮的联盟。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "老萧近况又是如何呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这是另一件头痛的事。自铁骑会烟消云散后，他便全力经略南方，土地幅员大增，兵力增至四十万，现时对我们虽仍是客客气气，但谁都不知他明天会否变卦。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "争霸天下，始终要看能否控制关外这片土地。我竹花帮的兄弟又如何？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "此事致致会比较清楚一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你真是关心你的兄弟，还是怕竹花帮从你的手心又飞走呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "若我仍是在扬州和小陵玩石子泥沙的年代，关心的当然只会是朋友。不过现在人长大了，自然要为自己的事业和将来着想，而朋友则是事业一个构成的主要部份，这么说够坦白了吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你的儿时玩伴桂锡良已成了竹花帮新帮主邵令周的快婿，手掌实权，满意了吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "柳菁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "还不多谢致致，她在此事上为你用了很多力气哩！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_qian",
      "speaker_name": "伏骞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此功夫，竟敢在本人面前班门弄斧，确是可笑之极。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好戏终于上演了。我们究竟该留在这里吃东西，还是去凑热闹呢？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "柳菁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "还用多想吗？",
      "tone": "嗔怪",
      "chapter": 194,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 373
    }
